## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Tech stack confirmation needed.** The plan uses **Vite + React + TypeScript** for the frontend and **Express + SQLite** for the backend. If you prefer a different framework (Next.js, Vue, PostgreSQL, etc.), please let me know before I begin.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Monorepo vs separate repos.** The plan uses a monorepo with `client/` and `server/` workspaces. Is this acceptable, or would you prefer separate repositories?

> [!WARNING]
> **Scope is large.** This is a 5-phase build. I will implement each phase sequentially and check in with you at key milestones. Phase 1 (scaffolding + core UI) will be built first.

